{
  "stem": "16571.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I would like to go back to my mother, because I'm keep on slipping, forgetting a few things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I learned since from my sisters that my mother, having no children of her own, and the lady next door which were neighbor, she had about-- obviously grown up children from about 20 downwards, but she had a lot of children. 10 at least, if not more.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother helped her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She took her a couple of her kids to carry on her-- her lap.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we believe to this day, my brother and-- and my sisters, that she was strong enough if she didn't have these kids she would have been selected for work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they didn't stop to ask, are they your kids, or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by having one, at least, if not two children in her arms, straight to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I will always believe that until the day I die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And talking about believing, I-- I still-- I think I mentioned it on the film before-- because my younger brother was taken off from my father, because he was after all four and a half years younger than me, I looked tall, big against him.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took him, and they said you're going back to your mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was selected for work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was still, in my mind, if I lived to 120, I believe if he wouldn't have been with us, if he would have gone with my mother, probably I would have been chosen because I next-- against my father, I was very little because my father was six foot plus.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's my belief, and I'm sticking to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And your-- your younger brother was told he was going off to his mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
